text: Zakia Parvin Khanam is a Bangladeshi politician who is elected as Member of 11th Jatiya Sangsad of Reserved Seats for Women. She is a politician of Bangladesh Awami League. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Awami League politicians Category:People from Netrokona District Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Women members of the Jatiya Sangsad
title: Zakia Parvin Khanam
